WEBVTT

00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:40.580
=Reincarnated Love=

00:00:40.780 --> 00:00:43.700
=Episode 11=

00:00:59.880 --> 00:01:01.320
Sign this divorce letter.

00:01:03.030 --> 00:01:04.150
Things are over between us.

00:01:05.180 --> 00:01:07.020
(Divorce Letter)

00:01:09.430 --> 00:01:10.510
Ruoli, I...

00:01:10.510 --> 00:01:11.350
Huo Linchuan,

00:01:11.840 --> 00:01:12.760
do you still remember

00:01:14.680 --> 00:01:15.520
the pact between us?

00:01:17.920 --> 00:01:19.200
You change my fated death;

00:01:20.710 --> 00:01:21.950
I protect your family.

00:01:23.290 --> 00:01:24.140
And what happened?

00:01:24.140 --> 00:01:26.340
♪Two swallows nest upon the beam♪

00:01:26.340 --> 00:01:28.640
♪Bringing fresh mud for the home♪

00:01:29.070 --> 00:01:30.120
I broke my word.

00:01:30.230 --> 00:01:32.510
♪Gazing afar at the roadside
that I once knew♪

00:01:32.510 --> 00:01:35.520
♪Lush grass swayed in abundance♪

00:01:35.710 --> 00:01:36.560
Between us,

00:01:37.656 --> 00:01:39.302
everything was wrong
from the very start.

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:41.240
Now,

00:01:42.230 --> 00:01:43.200
we are

00:01:44.120 --> 00:01:45.310
completely even.

00:01:46.680 --> 00:01:47.520
Perfect.

00:01:47.830 --> 00:01:48.670
Ruoli.

00:01:48.680 --> 00:01:49.520
Let go of me.

00:01:53.600 --> 00:01:55.220
♪That same gentle smile♪

00:01:55.220 --> 00:01:59.780
♪Each hides a trace of familiarity♪

00:02:00.190 --> 00:02:02.220
♪Let passions pour freely♪

00:02:02.220 --> 00:02:05.020
♪How much do you truly know♪

00:02:05.140 --> 00:02:07.990
♪I gift you a sprig of jasmine♪

00:02:07.990 --> 00:02:11.480
♪May we never part,
bound from dawn to dusk♪

00:02:11.480 --> 00:02:14.070
♪Who'd think parting comes so easily♪

00:02:14.590 --> 00:02:15.430
Have you truly

00:02:17.120 --> 00:02:18.030
made up your mind?

00:02:18.030 --> 00:02:20.250
♪You always cheer me up♪

00:02:21.710 --> 00:02:22.910
Yes.

00:02:24.720 --> 00:02:30.730
♪Falling into dreams,
this feeling lingers♪

00:02:42.910 --> 00:02:43.750
Mr. Huo.

00:02:44.960 --> 00:02:45.870
Mr. Huo,

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:47.640
bad news.

00:02:49.080 --> 00:02:50.240
Someone spread false orders.

00:02:50.560 --> 00:02:51.906
They pretended it was for the Duke

00:02:52.240 --> 00:02:53.360
and took all our men

00:02:53.360 --> 00:02:54.280
from the Jiang Mansion.

00:02:55.190 --> 00:02:56.560
Our brothers were all caught

00:02:57.710 --> 00:02:58.910
in an ambush on the outskirts.

00:02:59.870 --> 00:03:02.240
Send people to protect
Jiang Ruoli at once.

00:03:05.030 --> 00:03:06.910
If anything happens to her,

00:03:08.030 --> 00:03:10.080
all of you will pay for it.

00:03:11.590 --> 00:03:12.430
Yes.

00:03:17.580 --> 00:03:21.060
(Jiang Mansion)

00:03:30.680 --> 00:03:31.910
Isn't this Lady Ruoli?

00:03:31.910 --> 00:03:32.829
Why has she moved back?

00:03:32.840 --> 00:03:34.150
Did Mr. Huo divorce her?

00:03:40.700 --> 00:03:41.540
Oh.

00:03:41.560 --> 00:03:43.360
Isn't this Mrs. Huo?

00:03:43.560 --> 00:03:44.910
Were you kicked out?

00:03:46.310 --> 00:03:47.150
Why?

00:03:47.400 --> 00:03:48.710
Your husband abandoned you

00:03:49.080 --> 00:03:50.280
right after your parents died?

00:03:51.590 --> 00:03:52.813
Stop pretending to be so noble.

00:03:53.240 --> 00:03:54.710
You're just a discarded wife.

00:03:55.280 --> 00:03:56.470
How dare you come back?

00:03:57.030 --> 00:03:57.870
If I were you,

00:03:58.080 --> 00:03:59.470
I would've ended it long ago.

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:00.840
Get out.

00:04:02.120 --> 00:04:03.190
Don't be upset.

00:04:06.080 --> 00:04:07.100
(Invitation)
Ruoli,

00:04:07.120 --> 00:04:08.360
your parents just died,

00:04:08.680 --> 00:04:10.240
and you were kicked out.

00:04:10.910 --> 00:04:11.910
Father and I

00:04:12.150 --> 00:04:14.030
worried that you're alone,

00:04:14.430 --> 00:04:16.000
so we prepared this Spring Banquet,

00:04:16.190 --> 00:04:17.630
hoping you could come and relax.

00:04:19.040 --> 00:04:19.880
Shut up.

00:04:21.160 --> 00:04:22.050
Jiang Ruoli,

00:04:22.070 --> 00:04:22.920
you're no longer

00:04:22.930 --> 00:04:24.070
the honored Mrs. Huo.

00:04:24.300 --> 00:04:25.190
Things have changed.

00:04:25.190 --> 00:04:26.630
No one stands with you anymore.

00:04:30.270 --> 00:04:31.190
If you insult me again,

00:04:31.270 --> 00:04:32.680
you'll never speak in this lifetime.

00:04:32.870 --> 00:04:33.720
Jiang Ruoli, you...

00:04:34.030 --> 00:04:34.940
How dare you slap me?

00:04:34.950 --> 00:04:36.720
You deserved it
for forgetting your place.

00:04:39.190 --> 00:04:40.030
Remember this:

00:04:40.870 --> 00:04:42.480
As long as I'm still your cousin,

00:04:43.360 --> 00:04:44.920
you have no right to speak out of turn.

00:04:45.270 --> 00:04:46.110
Get lost.

00:04:52.100 --> 00:04:54.940
(Invitation)

00:04:55.750 --> 00:04:57.190
My parents just passed away,

00:04:59.070 --> 00:05:01.560
yet they rushed to hold a grand feast.

00:05:03.270 --> 00:05:04.360
How bold.

00:05:05.740 --> 00:05:07.940
(Jiang Mansion)

00:05:09.360 --> 00:05:10.560
Wanyue.

00:05:12.310 --> 00:05:13.150
Mr. Lu.

00:05:13.800 --> 00:05:14.650
- Try this.
- Milady.

00:05:16.360 --> 00:05:17.270
Lady Wanyue.

00:05:17.480 --> 00:05:18.950
You've arrived as promised.

00:05:18.950 --> 00:05:20.000
You didn't let me down.

00:05:20.720 --> 00:05:21.560
Where's Yuan?

00:05:23.240 --> 00:05:24.510
You came to see Jiang Ruoli?

00:05:25.270 --> 00:05:26.120
Is her mood

00:05:26.120 --> 00:05:27.560
a bit better now?

00:05:29.160 --> 00:05:30.070
She's alright.

00:05:30.070 --> 00:05:30.910
Please, come inside.

00:05:37.070 --> 00:05:39.630
(Jiang Ruoli, you always want)

00:05:39.630 --> 00:05:40.810
(to take everything from me.)

00:05:41.190 --> 00:05:42.120
(Fine.)

00:05:42.190 --> 00:05:43.120
(Very well.)

00:05:43.360 --> 00:05:46.040
(I'll make sure your reputation
is ruined soon.)

00:05:54.120 --> 00:05:55.600
The Chancellor has passed away.

00:05:55.600 --> 00:05:56.920
Now, Jiang Ruoli...

00:05:56.920 --> 00:05:58.160
Let's not speak of it.

00:05:58.240 --> 00:05:59.800
After Uncle passed away,

00:05:59.800 --> 00:06:01.630
my cousin moved back to live with us.

00:06:01.630 --> 00:06:03.040
Mr. Huo hasn't visited even once.

00:06:03.360 --> 00:06:04.630
She grieves day and night.

00:06:04.870 --> 00:06:05.920
As her cousin,

00:06:06.120 --> 00:06:07.440
it pains me to see her like this.

00:06:07.630 --> 00:06:08.470
What?

00:06:08.870 --> 00:06:10.720
Did the Huo clan abandon her?

00:06:11.070 --> 00:06:12.870
Will she still come today?

00:06:13.830 --> 00:06:14.830
Do we even need to ask?

00:06:15.270 --> 00:06:16.546
The Chancellor is gone;

00:06:16.557 --> 00:06:17.693
her husband has cast her out.

00:06:17.800 --> 00:06:19.430
Isn't she almost like a stray?

00:06:20.360 --> 00:06:21.630
If I were in her place,

00:06:21.630 --> 00:06:23.390
I'd hide myself away from everyone.

00:06:42.000 --> 00:06:43.680
I can't believe you came.

00:06:43.870 --> 00:06:45.950
I was just talking
with the other ladies.

00:06:47.160 --> 00:06:48.750
You recently lost your parents

00:06:48.750 --> 00:06:50.510
and had a quarrel with Mr. Huo.

00:06:50.510 --> 00:06:52.120
If I'd known you'd join us today,

00:06:52.120 --> 00:06:54.190
I would've waited to begin
until you arrived.

00:06:54.310 --> 00:06:55.800
I heard Lady Ruoli

00:06:55.870 --> 00:06:57.630
was sent home
in the middle of the night.

00:06:58.920 --> 00:07:00.560
It seems she only brought back

00:07:00.560 --> 00:07:01.560
a single handmaid

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:03.160
and two shabby bundles.

00:07:04.160 --> 00:07:05.680
Perhaps she's been cast aside.

00:07:07.390 --> 00:07:08.750
Left as a widow,

00:07:08.750 --> 00:07:10.800
without her husband to rely on,

00:07:10.800 --> 00:07:12.950
how will she manage from now on?

00:07:14.640 --> 00:07:15.480
Well.

00:07:15.480 --> 00:07:16.320
Ruoli,

00:07:16.320 --> 00:07:17.460
it was my fault.

00:07:17.480 --> 00:07:18.393
Please, don't be upset.

00:07:18.680 --> 00:07:19.920
Wanyue, that's not quite right.

00:07:20.800 --> 00:07:21.640
Mrs. Huo...

00:07:21.830 --> 00:07:22.670
No.

00:07:22.920 --> 00:07:24.830
It's Lady Ruoli now.

00:07:25.040 --> 00:07:26.390
She still holds a noble status,

00:07:26.560 --> 00:07:28.120
always looking down on others.

00:07:28.120 --> 00:07:30.190
Even if you care for sisterhood,

00:07:30.190 --> 00:07:31.040
I fear...

00:07:31.040 --> 00:07:31.880
Wanyue,

00:07:32.270 --> 00:07:34.950
did our expensive etiquette nanny

00:07:35.360 --> 00:07:37.246
only taught you to gossip
behind others' backs?

00:07:38.190 --> 00:07:39.430
How are you any different

00:07:39.430 --> 00:07:40.950
from street riffraff?

00:07:41.040 --> 00:07:42.270
How dare you insult me?

00:07:42.270 --> 00:07:43.390
Now, you're just...

00:07:46.800 --> 00:07:47.870
It seems

00:07:47.870 --> 00:07:49.360
you forgot the lesson you learned

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:51.310
in the prison last time.

00:07:51.330 --> 00:07:52.180
Jiang Ruoli,

00:07:52.190 --> 00:07:53.480
as a discarded woman...

00:07:58.160 --> 00:07:59.000
Your father

00:07:59.390 --> 00:08:02.480
took 100,000 taels
to take care of things

00:08:02.870 --> 00:08:04.800
from the military funds, right?

00:08:05.680 --> 00:08:06.680
Have you lost your mind?

00:08:09.870 --> 00:08:12.310
That mistress your father keeps outside

00:08:12.310 --> 00:08:14.680
gave birth to a son, right?

00:08:14.920 --> 00:08:16.360
Congratulations.

00:08:16.830 --> 00:08:17.750
What?

00:08:18.190 --> 00:08:19.030
Everyone,

00:08:20.040 --> 00:08:21.360
anyone else who wishes

00:08:21.360 --> 00:08:23.000
to discuss their family matters with me?

00:08:24.360 --> 00:08:25.200
Shameless woman!

00:08:37.320 --> 00:08:38.390
How dare you insult

00:08:38.750 --> 00:08:39.670
the daughter

00:08:40.150 --> 00:08:41.630
of late the Chancellor?

00:08:56.010 --> 00:08:56.870
Ruoli,

00:08:56.870 --> 00:08:57.710
are you alright?

00:08:58.510 --> 00:08:59.350
I'm fine.

00:09:00.440 --> 00:09:02.240
You don't have to carry all this alone.

00:09:03.240 --> 00:09:04.386
Just like when we were young,

00:09:04.510 --> 00:09:05.360
you can lean on me.

00:09:05.360 --> 00:09:06.240
Yunzhou,

00:09:07.120 --> 00:09:07.960
please, stop.

00:09:10.030 --> 00:09:11.336
We've known each other for years.

00:09:12.030 --> 00:09:13.080
In your heart,

00:09:13.320 --> 00:09:14.790
am I really only your brother?

00:09:16.200 --> 00:09:17.480
You only chose him

00:09:17.870 --> 00:09:19.360
to protect Uncle Jiang.

00:09:20.390 --> 00:09:21.720
Now that you two have parted,

00:09:22.390 --> 00:09:23.230
could you

00:09:25.240 --> 00:09:26.390
give me a chance?

00:09:27.670 --> 00:09:29.150
Yunzhou,

00:09:29.150 --> 00:09:30.550
I haven't avenged my father.

00:09:30.550 --> 00:09:31.390
Right now,

00:09:32.166 --> 00:09:33.659
I don't wish to discuss anything else.

00:09:36.270 --> 00:09:37.110
I understand.

00:09:37.720 --> 00:09:38.670
I spoke out of turn.

00:09:40.320 --> 00:09:41.440
If you ever need anything,

00:09:41.440 --> 00:09:42.910
I'll always be there for you.

00:09:47.960 --> 00:09:49.440
Well said.

00:09:50.510 --> 00:09:51.350
Yanzhi.

00:09:51.960 --> 00:09:54.000
You truly are devoted.

00:09:55.390 --> 00:09:56.230
You...

00:09:57.806 --> 00:09:59.166
I've always seen you as a brother.

00:09:59.790 --> 00:10:01.960
Unless I heard wrong just now,

00:10:01.960 --> 00:10:03.960
were you confessing to my wife?

00:10:04.750 --> 00:10:06.790
Yuan and I have made things clear.

00:10:06.790 --> 00:10:08.440
My care for her

00:10:08.440 --> 00:10:10.390
is only because we grew up together.

00:10:12.030 --> 00:10:13.840
Now, you accuse me without reason,

00:10:13.840 --> 00:10:14.960
casting blame upon me.

00:10:15.630 --> 00:10:17.063
Have you thought about her feelings?

00:10:20.670 --> 00:10:21.750
If you're just her brother,

00:10:23.030 --> 00:10:24.670
why ask her to give you a chance?

00:10:28.320 --> 00:10:29.160
That's enough.

00:10:32.080 --> 00:10:32.920
Huo Linchuan,

00:10:33.440 --> 00:10:35.440
stop accusing others.

00:10:35.853 --> 00:10:37.390
What right do you have to question him?

00:10:37.390 --> 00:10:38.630
What right do I have?

00:10:39.910 --> 00:10:41.670
You are

00:10:41.670 --> 00:10:42.870
my one and only wife.

00:10:43.600 --> 00:10:44.720
If anyone here

00:10:45.080 --> 00:10:46.360
dares speak carelessly

00:10:48.000 --> 00:10:49.360
or covet my wife,

00:10:51.390 --> 00:10:54.150
they'd be standing against the Huo clan.

00:10:56.910 --> 00:10:57.750
Huo Linchuan,

00:10:58.440 --> 00:11:00.150
we've divorced.

00:11:00.150 --> 00:11:00.990
Please...

00:11:01.360 --> 00:11:02.200
Ruoli.

00:11:02.270 --> 00:11:03.110
Huo Linchuan.

00:11:03.550 --> 00:11:04.710
- Ruoli.
- Huo Linchuan.

00:11:05.240 --> 00:11:06.080
Put me down.

00:11:07.030 --> 00:11:07.870
Let go.

00:11:08.440 --> 00:11:09.280
Let go!

00:11:37.740 --> 00:11:39.260
♪The dream shattered♪

00:11:39.620 --> 00:11:41.300
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

00:11:41.300 --> 00:11:42.940
♪Like a restless soul♪

00:11:43.820 --> 00:11:45.380
♪How vague♪

00:11:45.780 --> 00:11:47.300
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

00:11:47.300 --> 00:11:49.540
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

00:11:50.340 --> 00:11:52.940
♪Love and hate entwined♪

00:11:53.420 --> 00:11:56.260
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

00:11:56.900 --> 00:12:01.660
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

00:12:02.260 --> 00:12:03.780
♪When fate falls apart♪

00:12:04.180 --> 00:12:07.740
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

00:12:08.460 --> 00:12:10.020
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

00:12:10.420 --> 00:12:14.140
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

00:12:14.860 --> 00:12:17.700
♪Life after life♪

00:12:18.180 --> 00:12:20.860
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

00:12:21.500 --> 00:12:25.580
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

00:12:25.660 --> 00:12:28.700
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

00:12:28.860 --> 00:12:30.260
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

00:12:30.260 --> 00:12:33.380
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

00:12:33.460 --> 00:12:34.900
♪Now shatter apart♪

00:12:35.020 --> 00:12:38.780
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

00:12:39.500 --> 00:12:42.300
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

00:12:42.580 --> 00:12:45.420
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

00:12:45.740 --> 00:12:50.140
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

00:12:50.380 --> 00:12:53.300
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

00:12:53.420 --> 00:12:57.860
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

00:12:58.060 --> 00:13:03.780
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

00:13:04.220 --> 00:13:06.940
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

00:13:07.180 --> 00:13:09.900
♪Sober or indulge♪

00:13:10.340 --> 00:13:16.340
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪